author: ema
msg: [CXF-2723]:Reenable the ClientProxyFactoryBean and JAXWSClientFactoryBean configuration during port creation. This makes other Configurer implementation can replace the default dababinding with ClientProxyFactoryBean.getServiceFactory.setDatabinding(ownConfiguredDatabinding) in client side

author: rhuijben
msg: Following up upon r930191, also redirect CRT messages to STDERR
on Windows when compiling in _DEBUG modes, to allow continuing the
testsuite on this class of errors.
(svn_cmdline_init): Set all crt error handlers to log to stderr and the
debugger instead of to a dialog.
